## Form Accessibility

### Label Association
```css
/* Ensure all form inputs have associated labels */
.form-field {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.form-label {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
}

.form-label.required::after {
  content: " *";
  color: var(--danger);
}

/* For complex form layouts */
.form-label-inline {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-2);
}

/* Hidden labels for icon-only inputs */
.form-label.sr-only {
  position: absolute;
  width: 1px;
  height: 1px;
  padding: 0;
  margin: -1px;
  overflow: hidden;
  clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
  white-space: nowrap;
  border: 0;
}
```

