### Touch Target Sizes
```css
/* Minimum 44x44px touch targets */
.touch-target {
  min-width: 44px;
  min-height: 44px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
}

/* Expand touch area for small elements */
.icon-button {
  width: 24px;
  height: 24px;
  position: relative;
}

.icon-button::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -10px;
  left: -10px;
  right: -10px;
  bottom: -10px;
  /* Invisible but touchable area */
}

/* Adequate spacing between touch targets */
.button-group .button {
  margin: var(--space-2);
}

.button-group .button + .button {
  margin-left: var(--space-3);
}
```

